{"tid":1714934,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"急召海外大學香港留學生寫信要求校方支援中大外籍交流生","createTime":"2019-11-13T03:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T03:40:11.000Z","uid":322507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8a6df8450e68dea66b8429c0fac07285ede36c","tid":1714934,"uid":322507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ACT NOW Write to your faculty and university administration regarding exchange students at CUHK<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>急召海外大學香港留學生寫信要求校方支援中大外籍交流生</strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n尋日，香港警察正式攻打各大專院校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中喺中文大學嘅二號橋多個小時不斷施放催淚彈同橡膠彈<br />\n企圖攻入校園<br />\n更導致大學水源被化學品污染<br />\n全球多間院校都同中大有交流生計劃<br />\n<br />\n我哋呼籲所有喺院校嘅學生同教職員向校方寫信<br />\n<br />\n要求校方以行動確保交流生喺中大嘅安全 <br />\n譴責香港警察危害學生安全 <br />\n並要求領事館適時介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787775c67189d9932b6417ff8414727a18192113","tid":1714934,"uid":323954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"push.."}]}